'''马哈尼耶胡达市场'''（{{lang-he|שוק מחנה יהודה}}, ''Shuk Mahane Yehuda''）是[[以色列|以色列]][[耶路撒冷|耶路撒冷]]的一个市场，广受当地人和游客的欢迎，250多个摊位<ref name="foner">{{cite web |url=http://www.fonerbooks.com/guide_30.htm |title=Mahane Yehuda – The Jerusalem Shuk (Outdoor Market) |last=Rosenthal |first=Morris |date=May 2009 |accessdate=June 17, 2010 |publisher=Foner Books.com |archive-date=2011-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711015431/http://www.fonerbooks.com/guide_30.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>出售新鲜水果和蔬菜；焙烤食品；鱼，肉和奶酪；坚果，种子和香料；葡萄酒和烈酒；衣服和鞋子；和家用器皿，纺织品和犹太文物<ref name="mitnick">{{cite news|url=http://www.thejewishweek.com/special_sections/israel_now/whole_lotta_shuk_ing_going|title=Whole Lotta Shuk-ing Going On|first=Joshua|last=Mitnick|accessdate=July 3, 2011|publisher=[[The_Jewish_Week|The Jewish Week]]|date=February 27, 2008|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021145055/http://www.thejewishweek.com/special_sections/israel_now/whole_lotta_shuk_ing_going|archivedate=2012-10-21}}</ref><ref name="visiting">{{cite web |url=http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/News.aspx/133492 |title=Visiting the Mahane Yehuda Open Air Market |last=Browns |first=Shmuel |date=September 17, 2009 |accessdate=June 17, 2010 |publisher=israelnationalnews.com |archive-date=2017-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914022652/http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/News.aspx/133492 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。市场及其周围有出售[[油炸鷹嘴豆餅|油炸鷹嘴豆餅]]、沙威玛、[[烤肉|烤肉]]、肉串、[[库纳法|库纳法]]、[[巴卡拉|巴卡拉]]、酥糖和烧烤的摊位，果汁店，咖啡馆和餐馆。<ref name="foner"/> 

