==顾客==
市场的商店和餐馆（犹太和非犹太）吸引了居民和游客，耶路撒冷人和外地的以色列人，富人和穷人，年轻人和老年人，宗教和世俗，犹太人和非犹太人，包括阿拉伯人。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.haaretz.com/weekend/magazine/feeling-they-are-losing-jerusalem-orthodox-and-secular-jewish-residents-join-forces-1.415809 |last=Livneh |first=Nen |title=Feeling they are 'losing' Jerusalem, Orthodox and secular Jewish residents join forces|work=Haaretz |accessdate=September 6, 2012}}</ref>估计每周有20万人造访。 

==营业时间==
虽然马哈尼耶胡达市场内的一些餐馆和咖啡馆开到深夜，在安息日也开放。

==交通==
有数条公交线路服务于市场。[[耶路撒冷轻轨|耶路撒冷轻轨]]1号线在2011年8月开通，在雅法路市场对面设马哈尼耶胡达站<ref name="lr">{{cite web|url=http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/news/jerusalem-s-light-rail-system-opens-to-the-public-after-years-of-delays-1.379436|last=Rosenberg|first=Oz|title=Jerusalem's light rail system opens to the public after years of delays|work=Haaretz|date=August 19, 2011|accessdate=September 7, 2012|archive-date=2011-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110819050513/http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/news/jerusalem-s-light-rail-system-opens-to-the-public-after-years-of-delays-1.379436|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://forward.com/articles/144190/jerusalem-rail-brings-city-closer-together/ |last=Jeffay|first=Nathan|title=Jerusalem rail brings city closer together|work=[[The_Forward|The Forward]]|date=October 14, 2011|accessdate=September 7, 2012}}</ref> 
